{"tid":1673834,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"李嘉欣生B收1億現金","createTime":"2019-10-25T01:20:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T09:30:19.000Z","uid":48905,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"742e2754b52fdc5ed7f0a9be3938376f27c957eb","tid":1673834,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T01:20:30.000Z","msg":"女人要經歷十月懷胎及十級痛楚，才可誕下肥肥白白的BB，認真偉大！不少女星更獲老公送贈豐厚禮物，以作生B鼓勵！<br />\n<br />\n楊思琦姑媽的姨甥女、「大美人」李嘉欣於2008年與許晉亨結婚，2011年誕下兒子許建彤，有指當時獲老公送1億港元現金及價值200萬的鑽戒。李嘉欣老公許晉亨雖然是許家接班人，但是他的爸爸許世勳於離世前早已將430億港元的遺產撥入家族信託基金，並由專業經理人經營，家族成員並沒有直接得到遺產。即使家族背景雄厚，李嘉欣和許晉亨兩夫婦現時「只能」每月透過基金「領取」約200萬港元生活費。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JQ5jBuC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJQ5jBuC.jpg&h=abb46ce7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86be4b88580104224e315be982f88340ca94fa7f","tid":1673834,"uid":4596,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T01:23:50.000Z","msg":"得2M 聞者傷心 聽者流淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e39b406870d7807cd70d398f8b4b0e7fb052c0e4","tid":1673834,"uid":16326,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T01:25:36.000Z","msg":"每月200萬生活費 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n這些機會.........."},{"pid":"3c724afae272576aead8d93450f155b28eb39a05","tid":1673834,"uid":6674,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T01:29:46.000Z","msg":"我真係恭喜你呀"},{"pid":"6f5077dfc422b941e60ec5f6383d810573ebf5cc","tid":1673834,"uid":61520,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T01:30:57.000Z","msg":"關我撚事咩， 有無捐啲俾星火？？？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今日星期五喇 你哋知唔知星期日有遊行㗎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1673577\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1673577</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span>"},{"p